data.description:
Beautiful ranch style newer home. Very well maintained. A floor plan with large family room that opens to the kitchen space with a
large island. Kitchen includes all stainless-steel appliances. This home features lots of cabinet and counter space in the kitchen. Oversized sliding glass doors from dining room to backyard patio. Lots of natural light in the kitchen, living room and dining room areas. Both the back and front yard are fully landscaped with sprinklers and fencing. The back yard is currently covered with turf. The primary suite features dual sinks and a large walk in closet. There is also plenty of room for storage in the crawl space with a concrete floor. This property also has solar panels, so you can enjoy immediate energy savings. Easy access to I-70 and DIA.
